data.text: @h2owizet @TonyMoonbeam Didn't Manchin endorse Biden too? That doesn't mean much.
@TonyMoonbeam @MJRosenbergDad Manchin endorses Lamb. We know what a thorn Manchin has been for us. Lamb is his guy. Worries me.
@TonyMoonbeam It's important to keep in mind that these 2 men are running a joint campaign.

@TonyMoonbeam I think if elected, both of them would represent the state just fine and be reliable votes in the Senate.

The question is, can either of them actually win?

Neither of these doofuses has done anything concrete for their state. I've seen accounts claim that @malcolmkenyatta has introduced hundreds of bills in the PA legislature. Word? How many were signed into law? Oh none? What are we even doing here?
